modDescription:
Replaced the in game Eric’s Stuff (oldwest\_business\_07) with Eric’s Goods to add challenge, [quest](https://7daystodiemods.com/tag/7-days-to-die-quests/), and loot to the otherwise cute but very boring POI.

**[Download](https://github.com/Laotseu/7dtdMods/releases/download/EricsGoods_v1.0/EricsGoods_v1.0.zip)**

The forum topic of the mod is [here](https://community.7daystodie.com/topic/19462-motorcyclealterations-v10-alpha-18/).
